                            <comment id="17794657" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 8 Dec 2023 11:59:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;From the release notes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fixed vulnerability of a potential denial of service attack on a centralized logback receiver when a third party controlling a remote appender connects to said receiver and could shut down or slow down logging of events.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We don&apos;t offer logback in a remote configuration so I suggest we suppress.&lt;/p&gt;

